          "blocks": {
            "text_bPbJ4x": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>The anorak is a lightweight, casual jacket, which has the single express purpose of being easy to pull over the head, keep out the wind and rain, and allow the body to move and breathe. It goes about this in a fairly interesting and roundabout way: simple on its face but in fact very much not.</p>",
